Class AbstractPingAwareQuorumFunction

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.hazelcast.quorum.impl.AbstractPingAwareQuorumFunction
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    HazelcastInstanceAware, MembershipListener, PingAware, EventListener
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ProbabilisticQuorumFunction, RecentlyActiveQuorumFunction

    public abstract class AbstractPingAwareQuorumFunction
extends Object
implements PingAware, HazelcastInstanceAware, MembershipListener
    Base class for quorum functions which may use ICMP failure detector information to determine presence of quorum.
